    "title": "UK targets Gazprom pipelines with new export controls",
    "url": "https://example.com/uk-gazprom-controls",
    "publication_date": "2024-11-25",
    "snippet": "The UK government introduced licensing requirements for any cargoes transiting Gazprom‑controlled pipelines, aiming to reduce Russian gas flow into Europe."
  },
  {
    "title": "Swiss financial watchdog freezes assets of Russian oil majors",
    "url": "https://example.com/swiss-freeze-oil",
    "publication_date": "2024-11-24",
    "snippet": "Swiss authorities seized $1.2 billion in assets belonging to several Russian oil firms, limiting their ability to refinance projects abroad."
  },
  {
    "title": "Japan joins G7 in restricting Russian energy equipment exports",
    "url": "https://example.com/japan-g7-restrictions",
    "publication_date": "2024-11-23",
